---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="About the Author | TaxDebtWealthSuite"
  description="Meet the financial experts and software architects behind TaxDebtWealthSuite's proprietary calculators and planning tools."
>
  <main class="flex-grow max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest bg-[#00F5D4]/10 text-[#00F5D4] border border-[#00F5D4]/20 mb-4">The Team</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">About the Author</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-8">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-2 border-[#00F5D4]/30 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/author-mrittunjoy.png" alt="Mrittunjoy Das" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-center sm:text-left space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Mrittunjoy Das</h2>
          <p class="text-[#00F5D4] font-medium">Finance Enthusiast & Tool Architect</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Building free interactive math engines to simplify compound debt payoffs, asset-borrowing loopholes, and corporate tax tracking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Our Expertise</h3>
        <p>
          The calculators on this site are built using official formulas provided by major global tax authorities, including the IRS (United States), HMRC (United Kingdom), CRA (Canada), and ATO (Australia). Our developers hold deep expertise in algorithmic finance, ensuring that complex compounding interest formulas and marginal tax brackets are calculated with exact precision.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Why We Built This</h3>
        <p>
          We believe that advanced financial strategies shouldn't be locked behind expensive wealth management paywalls. Strategies like "Buy, Borrow, Die" or mathematically optimized Debt Avalanches are accessible to anyone who understands the math. We build these tools so you can run the numbers yourself, in complete privacy.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
